; Balance assertions should respect date ordering, not file ordering.
; A balance assertion on a posting dated 2010-01-02 should check the
; balance as of that date, even when placed after a 2010-01-03
; transaction in the file.

2010-01-01 * Starting Balance
    Assets:Bank:Checking        1000.00 EUR
    Equity:Opening-Balances

2010-01-02 * Shopping
    Expenses:Shopping           10 EUR
    Assets:Bank:Checking

2010-01-03 * Some more shopping
    Expenses:Shopping           5 EUR
    Assets:Bank:Checking

; verify balance as of 2010-01-02
2010-01-02 * Balance Check
    Assets:Bank:Checking        0 EUR    = 990.00 EUR

test bal Assets
          985.00 EUR  Assets:Bank:Checking
end test
